# SaaS and Subscription Retention Analytics Suite

## Overview

This project is a professional Streamlit Business Intelligence dashboard developed using the Telco Customer Churn dataset.

The dashboard provides insights into:

- Churn rates and retention trends
- Customer cohorts by signup tenure and lifecycle stage
- Customer lifetime patterns and LTV dynamics
- Key retention drivers and structural risk factors
- Business KPIs and financial health metrics



## Features

- Interactive Filters (Contract, Tech Infrastructure, Billing Mix)
- KPI Cards (Active Subscriptions, Gross Churn, MRR At Risk, Avg LTV)
- Responsive Layout
- Plotly Visualisations (Bar charts, survival distributions, pricing box plots)
- Customer Analytics
- Product Analytics
- Business Recommendations and Operational Save-List Pipeline



## Installation

```bash
pip install streamlit pandas plotly openpyxl

streamlit run app_1.py
